we can haul it,

15:39.806 --> 15:42.040
We're gonna haul it.

15:42.108 --> 15:46.044
[narrator] <i> fighting against</i>
<i> strong currents in</i>
<i> the deep trough of the fjord</i>

15:46.046 --> 15:49.113
<i> Captain wild bill attempts t</i>
<i> deal some frontier justice</i>

15:49.849 --> 15:51.916
<i> To the invasive russian reds</i>

15:54.421 --> 15:58.056
[tobias]

15:59.459 --> 16:01.459
